t;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1365424745&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-09-29\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1976-09-29.jpg?fit=500%2C497&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-13088 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1976-09-29.jpg?resize=500%2C497&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1976-09-29.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1976-09-29.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1976-09-29.jpg?resize=300%2C298&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1976-09-29.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/05/08/roll-of-the-dice-rendezvous/\">Rendezvous</a>&#8221; and &#8220;Someday (We&#8217;ll Be Together)&#8221; at The Record Plant in New York City. They will remain in the vault for decades until Bruce finally completes and releases them in 2010.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0ena3tWYo-g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RD0ena3tWYo-g\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZKFREGdtncg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDZKFREGdtncg\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>The Darkness Tour moves on to Boutwell Memorial Auditorium in Birmingham. <span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">(Photo credit: William E. Allen)</span></p>\n<div id=\"v-PNdFeC4l-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/PNdFeC4l?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54575\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/birmingham_post_herald_1978_09_30_19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Birmingham_Post_Herald_1978_09_30_19-scaled.jpg?fit=2122%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2122,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Birmingham_Post_Herald_1978_09_30_19\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Birmingham_Post_Herald_1978_09_30_19-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C914&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-54575 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Birmingham_Post_Herald_1978_09_30_19-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C914&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"914\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4561\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0929/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0929.jpg?fit=405%2C609&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"405,609\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0929\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0929.jpg?fit=405%2C609&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4561 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0929.jpg?resize=405%2C609&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"405\" height=\"609\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0929.jpg?w=405&amp;ssl=1 405w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0929.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 405px) 100vw, 405px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays two songs (although this is up for debate) with Billy Rancher &amp; The Unreal Gods on stage at On Broadway in Westwood, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of four shows at the final stand of the Born in the U.S.A. Tour in Los Angeles. In attendance tonight: The cast of television&#8217;s\u00a0<em>Growing Pains</em>.</p>\n<div id=\"v-Tu2dlnHp-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Tu2dlnHp?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29723\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-09-29-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-09-29.jpg?fit=584%2C824&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"584,824\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600700821&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-09-29\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-09-29.jpg?fit=584%2C824&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29723 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-09-29.jpg?resize=584%2C824&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"584\" height=\"824\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-09-29.jpg?w=584&amp;ssl=1 584w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-09-29.jpg?resize=213%2C300&amp;ssl=1 213w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1987:\u00a0</strong>Bruce rehearses with Roy Orbison at the Cocoanut Grove in Los Angeles for the filming of <em>Black &amp; White Night</em> the following day.</p>\n<p><strong>1989:</strong> Bruce makes a pit-stop at Matt&#8217;s Saloon in Prescott, Arizona while on a motorcycle trip from Los Angeles, joining house band Mile High Band on stage for about an hour and befriending and changing the life of a bartender before heading off to the Grand Canyon.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ordKJO1_Rxg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4564\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-0929/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1