on=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1989-09-29a.jpg?fit=513%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29721 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1989-09-29a.jpg?resize=758%2C1513&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1513\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1989-09-29a.jpg?w=926&amp;ssl=1 926w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1989-09-29a.jpg?resize=150%2C300&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1989-09-29a.jpg?resize=513%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 513w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1989-09-29a.jpg?resize=768%2C1533&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1989-09-29a.jpg?resize=770%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 770w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21500\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-09-29b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-29b.jpg?fit=420%2C817&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"420,817\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600701161&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1989-09-29b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-29b.jpg?fit=420%2C817&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21500 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-29b.jpg?resize=420%2C817&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"420\" height=\"817\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-29b.jpg?w=420&amp;ssl=1 420w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-29b.jpg?resize=154%2C300&amp;ssl=1 154w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new band play the San Diego Sports Arena on World Tour 1992.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/c-IWG0XJeWk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/96jehWdf8BM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1996:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays with Pete Seeger for the very first time at a Woody Guthrie tribute concert in Cleveland, along with Joe Ely, Arlo Guthrie, Ani DiFranco, the Indigo Girls, and more.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"