51&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"448\" height=\"1851\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2016-09-29a.jpg?w=448&amp;ssl=1 448w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2016-09-29a.jpg?resize=248%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 248w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2016-09-29a.jpg?resize=372%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 372w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds his first and only dress rehearsal (invite-only) for Springsteen on Broadway at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21521\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2017-09-29/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?fit=1462%2C1646&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1462,1646\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600715804&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2017-09-29\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?fit=758%2C853&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21521 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?resize=758%2C853&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"853\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?w=1462&amp;ssl=1 1462w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?resize=266%2C300&amp;ssl=1 266w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?resize=910%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 910w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?resize=768%2C865&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-09-29.jpg?resize=1364%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1364w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. Patti is absent again tonight, so Bruce adds an extra encore of &#8220;This Hard Land&#8221; in place of his duet of &#8220;Tougher Than the Rest&#8221; with Patti. In attendance tonight: Hozier.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21504\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2018-09-29/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-09-29.jpg?fit=499%2C502&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"499,502\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600702616&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2018-09-29\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-09-29.jpg?fit=499%2C502&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21504 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-09-29.jpg?resize=499%2C502&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"502\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-09-29.jpg?w=499&amp;ssl=1 499w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-09-29.jpg?resize=298%2C300&amp;ssl=1 298w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-09-29.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-09-29.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2022: </strong>Bruce announces his twenty-first studio album,\u00a0<em>Only the Strong Survive</em>, and releases a video for the album&#8217;s lead single, &#8220;Do I Love You (Indeed I Do).&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/O0jBwk71Qcw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>That evening, Bruce and Patti perform &#8220;The Promised Land&#8221; at the first annual Albie Awards, sponsored by The Clooney Foundation for Justice.</p>\n<div id=\"v-qpFXGq2N-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='758' src='https://videopress.com/embed/qpFXGq2N?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube